page.title: 09A KEELBY SATURDAY
page.content: A normal Saturday morning for me is that I would get up at half past 10 (because I am very lazy).I get down stairs about 25 mins to 11 and watch The Saturday Morning Picture Show until quarter past 12.At about half past 10 (the same time as me) my mum and dad get up.If we all get up late we have breakfast about quater past 11.For breakfast I normaly have a bowl of Rice Krispies and 1 or 2 crumpets.After breakfast I go back to my bed-room and change out of my night clothes into my day clothes. After dinner I normally have a game of tennis with Esme.Icome in about five o clock and have my tea which is usually a salad with fish.When I have finished my tea I watch the television.At about half past 7 an Ice cream van comes round and I sometimes have an Ice cream.
